parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view camera display can cause reduced visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The LCD display flickers or goes completely black
making it difficult or impossible to see the rear view camera feed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the interior trim and leather can lead to a compromised airbag system, potentially causing injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The stitching on the dash and leather around the airbag comes apart
compromising the structural integrity of the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential assembly can cause loss of control, accidents, or injuries due to the vehicle's inability to maintain traction and stability.
symptoms: The vehicle produces a loud whine or gear/bearing noise
and the "Service Rear Axle" or "Rear Axle System Off" warning indicator appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Infotainment System and Radio Display Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system and radio display can cause distracted driving, accidents, or injuries due to the flickering or rolling screen.
symptoms: The infotainment system and radio display flicker or roll
causing a distraction while driving
and the rear view camera display also flickers
making it difficult to back up safely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel leak and tank damage can cause fires, accidents, or injuries due to the risk of fuel igniting or the vehicle stalling.
symptoms: Fuel leaks from the rear differential or fuel tank
and the fuel filler neck tube collapses
causing leaks during fill-up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unusual noise and vibration can cause loss of control, accidents, or injuries due to the vehicle's instability.
symptoms: The vehicle produces a clicking or popping noise when turning slowly
which can be alarming and distracting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The frame failure and welding issues can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to the vehicle's compromised structural integrity.
symptoms: The frame shatters and falls apart at the welded connections
leaving occupants exposed and vulnerable to injury.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel odor and leak can cause fires, accidents, or injuries due to the risk of fuel igniting or the vehicle stalling.
symptoms: Strong fuel odors fill the garage and seep into the house
indicating a potential fuel leak.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel tank cracking and leaking can cause a fire hazard, putting the driver and others at risk of serious injury or death.
symptoms: Strong gasoline fume smell
fuel leaking from the left rear side of the vehicle
fuel puddles under the vehicle
fuel smell in the garage or house
difficulty filling the tank
gas smell lingering for days.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, fail to shift gears, or even lead to accidents due to loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle misfires
transmission overheating
failure to shift gears
loss of power
grinding or hesitation when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective driveline can cause the vehicle to vibrate violently, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: Engine shakes violently
whole car vibrates
driveline failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can lead to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities due to the loss of stopping power.
symptoms: Brake fading
brake fluid boiling out
automatic transmission overheating warning light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden loss of power and steering can cause accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle loses power when turning the steering wheel
power cuts off when using turn signals.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the manual transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, fail to shift gears, or even lead to accidents due to loss of control.
symptoms: 2nd gear synchronizer failure
grinding or hesitation when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, breakdown, or even engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine temperature quickly increases to unsafe temperatures
especially when idling or traveling at low speeds and in low gears
coolant level is full
steam emanating from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Infotainment center becomes inoperable
GPS and backup camera are inoperable
radio flickers and screen rolls
display goes blank periodically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various warning indicators to illuminate, leading to driver distraction, and potentially causing accidents or breakdowns.
symptoms: Various warning indicators illuminate on the instrument panel
vehicle begins to fishtail
analog gauges work at all times
display goes blank periodically
analog gauges go full scale and all warning lights illuminate for a few seconds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also lead to a loss of critical vehicle information.
symptoms: DIC display goes blank periodically
analog gauges work at all times
display becomes operative after driving for a period of time
display does not come on when opening the left door.
